data.description: This charming home offers incredible potential for those willing to roll up their sleeves and unleash its hidden beauty. With its original two-story structure boasting three bedrooms and a bath, complemented by a modern master suite added in 2005, this property offers a blend of historic character and contemporary convenience. Spread across multiple levels, including a library for quiet retreats and a spacious family room, this home offers ample room for comfortable living and entertaining. Enjoy the tranquility of the covered front porch and the generous 136 ft deep lot, perfect for gardening, outdoor activities, or potential expansion. Although lacking a garage, the property includes a convenient storage shed to accommodate your organizational needs. Look beyond the clutter to envision the remarkable possibilities awaiting within this home, where a little TLC can transform it into your perfect home.
